宇航员在出发前就进入了休眠状态
men have been put into hibernation before departure.

336
01:00:15,170 --> 01:00:16,700
为何这样安排
Why was this done?

337
01:00:16,980 --> 01:00:20,510
这样安排是为了最大限度地储存
Well, this was done in order to achieve the maximum conservation

338
01:00:20,510 --> 01:00:23,990
我们的生命维持资源  主要是食物和空气
of our life-support capabilities, basically food and air.

339
01:00:24,200 --> 01:00:28,010
正在休眠的三名航天员属于调查小组
Now the three hibernating crew members represent the survey team.

340
01:00:27,800 --> 01:00:31,770
{\an8\pos(182,63)\b1\shad0\bord0\fs15\fax0\frz222\c&H000000&\b1}卡明斯基博士

